   Effective March 19, 1999 the Commission on Structural Alternatives for
       the Federal Courts of Appeals completed its business and ceased
      operations. This Website will be maintained in its current status
      through the current session of Congress. Questions regarding the
    Commission's work, including requests for copies of the Commission's
     Report or its Working Papers, may be directed to the Administrative
             Office of the United States Courts at 202-502-1520.

